list.name: Default
list.comment: Couple of changes needed to put in the new multiple objective system, committing to be able to do a merge later.

task.summary: Periodic logging of brainwave data should work properly now
Changes to logging format (including adding logging for game state and score), started adding training view, ...
Added training course, increasing difficulty. Further improved logging.
Added lots of debug logging, fixed some things, ...
Fixed bugs and crashes testers were having. Made it impossible to make matches in between levels (that was also the cause of one of the bugs).
Added part of the signal processing and machine learning stuff, very much WIP.

Waaay too much to sum up in a single commit message (this should probably have been like... 10 or 20 commits...). Imported the mindwavemobile library, added the AutoEncoder code (not finished yet but it's close), bunch of other stuff. Also removed tons of bugs from the game code.

The AutoTransformer stuff should work now, I did change it to batch in stead of online learning for the time being, still have to try different settings to get the durn thang to learn properly (it's confused by a difference in available data for the different stages at the moment). I'm starting work on changing certain aspects of the game itself.

Changed the colors of the fruit based on user feedback, also changed size of 1. Added new objectives sidebar, new objectives aren't yet available though. Added a script that does grid search for the classifier, specifically made to be run on my DO droplet. To write that script I had to rewrite a lot of ml.learning, so it's a lot more general now.
Couple of changes needed to put in the new multiple objective system, committing to be able to do a merge later.
